{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-index-js","path":"/","result":{"data":{"hero":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Innovative Mind: Meet","name":"Sadiq Ahmed","subtitle":"Crafting App Magic","buttonText":"Contact Me"},"html":"<p>Web Architect ️ | PHP | Building innovative sites: Portfolios, Stores, &#x26; More | Let's innovate!</p>"}}]},"about":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"About Me","avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/ea4ab/me.jpg","srcSet":"/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/477ba/me.jpg 175w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/06776/me.jpg 350w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/ea4ab/me.jpg 700w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/3055e/me.jpg 1050w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/eff08/me.jpg 1400w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/c7213/me.jpg 6112w","srcWebp":"/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/89afa/me.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/9fca7/me.webp 175w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/37a4e/me.webp 350w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/89afa/me.webp 700w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/78e7a/me.webp 1050w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/03d34/me.webp 1400w,\n/static/8e00420755c18eb5220e0d1c3777fc31/20286/me.webp 6112w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}},"skills":["Laravel 10","PHP 8","JavaScript","Mysql","CSS","HTML","Nginx","Apache","Linux","Python"]},"html":"<p>Backend Mastermind: Building Web Solutions Tailored to You\r\nCrafting robust and dynamic web applications is my passion. As a full-stack developer with over 3 years of experience, I specialize in backend development, wielding PHP and Laravel like second nature. I'm your go-to guy for creating:</p>\n<p>=> Portfolio websites: Showcase your skills and impress potential clients with a website that reflects your unique personality.</p>\n<p>=> Ecommerce websites: Bring your business online with a seamless and secure platform for your customers to shop with ease.</p>\n<p>=> Business Management Systems: Streamline your operations and boost efficiency with custom-built tools for managing tasks, data, and workflows.</p>\n<p>=> Custom web projects: No project is too complex! Share your vision, and I'll translate it into a web solution that exceeds your expectations.</p>\n<p>I'm not just about code; I'm a collaborative partner who prioritizes understanding your needs and translating them into user-friendly, scalable solutions.\r\nConnect with me today to discuss your next web project!</p>\n<p>Here is a list of the technologies that I'm familiar with!</p>"}}]},"jobs":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Backend Developement","company":"Laravel","range":"-","url":"https://www.laravel.com/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Laravel is a free open-source PHP framework. It provides web developers tools and resources for building modern PHP web applications.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Laravel has useful built-in features like the Artisan command-line interface (CLI), native authentication and model-view-controller (MVC) architecture. These features make the framework easy to use and are the main reason for its popularity.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Laravel is a trendy web framework. It has more than 70,000 stars on GitHub and has become an in-demand skill on the job market.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Backend Developement","company":"PHP","range":"March 2019 - Present","url":"https://www.php.net/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The PHP Hypertext Preprocessor (PHP) is a programming language that allows web developers to create dynamic content that interacts with databases. PHP is basically used for developing web based software applications. This tutorial helps you to build your base with PHP.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>PHP is a server side scripting language that is embedded in HTML. It is used to manage dynamic content, databases, session tracking, even build entire e-commerce sites. It is integrated with a number of popular databases, including MySQL, PostgreSQL, Oracle, Sybase, Informix, and Microsoft SQL Server.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Web Development","company":"JS","range":"-","url":"#"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>JavaScript (JS) is a lightweight, interpreted, or just-in-time compiled programming language with first-class functions. While it is most well-known as the scripting language for Web pages, many non-browser environments also use it, such as Node.js, Apache CouchDB and Adobe Acrobat. JavaScript is a prototype-based, multi-paradigm, single-threaded, dynamic language, supporting object-oriented, imperative, and declarative (e.g. functional programming) styles.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>JavaScript's dynamic capabilities include runtime object construction, variable parameter lists, function variables, dynamic script creation (via eval), object introspection (via for...in and Object utilities), and source-code recovery (JavaScript functions store their source text and can be retrieved through toString()).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}}]},"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Alkane PHP","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.7857142857142858,"src":"/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/60290/demo.png","srcSet":"/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/847ef/demo.png 175w,\n/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/91cba/demo.png 350w,\n/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/60290/demo.png 700w,\n/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/ab559/demo.png 736w","srcWebp":"/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/89afa/demo.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/9fca7/demo.webp 175w,\n/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/37a4e/demo.webp 350w,\n/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/89afa/demo.webp 700w,\n/static/2398bc1a155a2fe9aa2c092d7ddaeef6/50b4d/demo.webp 7